nload PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 17, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dab1665702917106.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dab1665702917106.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dab1665702917106.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dab1665702917106\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Insert a new record.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dab1665702917106__section_ngj_y5r_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d942273e49\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130778e1_d130779e1_d130780e1\">Insert a new record in the table.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130781e1_d130782e1_d130783e1\">If the DBMS supports PRAs, Fetch the address of the\n        inserted record.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130784e1_d130785e1_d130786e1\">Build the primary key of the inserted record. Add the\n        primary key and, if available, the PRA to the hitlist by means of the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">uaddhit</code> service function.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dab1665702917106__section_i3t_dky_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d942273e67\">From Uniface</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Preconditions realized by Uniface—the table that <code class=\"ph codeph\">Write</code> is requested for is\n        open.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Information Available from Uniface</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\">Data Structure-&gt;Element</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;TMEnabled</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Indicates whether the connector is\n                TM-controlled.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrv</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Points to the connector workspace if a workspace was\n                requested in the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Info</code> request.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrvini</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Unique identification of the current logon\n                path.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;iobuf</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Points to the general I/O buffer which contains the\n                data to insert.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udatlen</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Length of the data pointed to by\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;iobuf</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;ufldlst</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">Field list that describes all the fields in the\n                table.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;vsfnr</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15659e1_d15660e1_d15661e1__entry__2\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">vsfnr</code> equals 0, this indicates\n                that segmented fields do not have to be inserted, otherwise they do have to be\n                inserted.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dab1665702917106__section_izf_2ky_bcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d942273e189\">To Uniface</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Connector Request Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__2\">Commit was successful.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__1\">-6</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__2\">Exceptional error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__1\">-7</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__2\">Write failed due to duplicate primary key.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__1\">-9</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__2\">I/O server logon error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__1\">-16</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dab1665702917106__table_d15662e1_d15663e1_d15664e1__entry__2\">DBMS reported network error.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130796e1_d130797e1_d130798e1\">When the connector request return value is less than\n        0, an error code must be supplied in <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;udrverr</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dab1665702917106__section_rnf_bvr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d942273e274\">Service Functions</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dab1665702917106__ul_wxp_bvr_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dab1665702917106__li_d46898e1_d46899e1_d46900e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wcr1665702917956.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcr1665702917956.html\" title=\"ubldprm builds the concatenated primary key for a record.\">ubldprm</a>\n</code>— Build the primary key.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dab1665702917106__li_d46901e1_d46902e1_d46903e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kut1665702917676.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kut1665702917676.html\" title=\"Adds an entry to the Uniface hitlist, or updates an existing one.\">uaddhit</a>\n</code>— Add a record to the hitlist.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dab1665702917106__section_c4v_2vr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d942273e307\">Extra information</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130805e1_d130806e1_d130807e1\">Uniface assumes that the DBMS checks the uniqueness of\n        keys in unique indexes (Uniface primary key and candidate keys).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130808e1_d130809e1_d130810e1\">When the connector has to insert segmented fields\n          (<code class=\"ph codeph\">vsfnr</code> is not equal to 0), the segments of the segmented field have to be\n        obtained directly from the Uniface kernel using the <code class=\"ph codeph\">ugetblob</code> service\n        function.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dab1665702917106__section_qtz_bvr_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d942273e326\">TM-Controlled Connectors</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dab1665702917106__p_d130733e1_d130734e1_d130735e1\">TM-controlled connectors are not allowed to begin,\n        commit or rollback transactions.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/afo1665702918517.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ugetblob</a><p>Get segmented data from the Uniface kernel.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kut1665702917676.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uaddhit</a><p>Adds an entry to the Uniface hitlist, or updates an existing one.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526705\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Write ('W') Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 17, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Insert a new record. Description Insert a new record in the table. If the DBMS supports PRAs, Fetch the address of the inserted record. Build the primary key of the inserted record. Add the primary key and, if available, the PRA to the hitlist by means of the uaddhit service function. From Uniface Preconditions realized by Uniface—the table that Write is requested for is open. Table 1. Information Available from Uniface Data Structure->Element Description uctrl->TMEnabled Indicates whether the connector is TM-controlled. uctrl->udrv Points to the connector workspace if a workspace was requested in the Info request. uctrl->udrvini Unique identification of the current logon path. uctrl->iobuf Points to the general I/O buffer which contains the data to insert. uctrl->udatlen Length of the data pointed to by uctrl->iobuf . uctrl->ufldlst Field list that describes all the fields in the table. uctrl->vsfnr If vsfnr equals 0, this indicates that segmented fields do not have to be inserted, otherwise they do have to be inserted. To Uniface Table 2. Connector Request Return Values Value Description 0 Commit was successful. -6 Exceptional error. -7 Write failed due to duplicate primary key. -9 I/O server logon error. -16 DBMS reported network error. When the connector request return value is less than 0, an error code must be supplied in uctrl->udrverr . Service Functions ubldprm — Build the primary key. uaddhit — Add a record to the hitlist. Extra information Uniface assumes that the DBMS checks the uniqueness of keys in unique indexes (Uniface primary key and candidate keys). When the connector has to insert segmented fields ( vsfnr is not equal to 0), the segments of the segmented field have to be obtained directly from the Uniface kernel using the ugetblob service function. TM-Controlled Connectors TM-controlled connectors are not allowed to begin, commit or rollback transactions. Related Links ugetblob Get segmented data from the Uniface kernel. uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. uaddhit Adds an entry to the Uniface hitlist, or updates an existing one. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}